metadata.name: Immune
metadata.description:
I present my first open edition; Immune.  
 
An NFT project that takes a personal look at the dangers of consumerism and the tactics used by corporations to keep us addicted. This project is a result of my own journey of self-discovery and my desire to challenge the societal norms that have been imposed upon us. I believe it's time to shed light on the dark intentions of corporations that prioritize profits over the health of our planet and its people. Through "Immune," I invite you to join me on this journey of self-awareness and to question the impact of your consumption patterns on your well-being. 

Let's BURN ties with materialism and reclaim our independence from corporations that seek to control us.
